    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 📊 Fetch Scheduled Posts\n\n**Reads Google Sheets** to find posts ready to publish.\n\n**Filter criteria:**\n- Status = \"Listo para postear\"\n- Returns only the first match\n\n**Required columns:**\n- Title, Copy, Video Link\n- Status, Fecha.Hora\n- row_number (for tracking)",
        "height": 544,
