    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🕐 Time Formatter\n\n**Converts trigger timestamp** to Spanish readable format.\n\n**Output example:**\n\"16 de Octubre a las 9 am\"\n\n**Includes:**\n- Day of week (Spanish)\n- Month name (Spanish)\n- 12-hour format with AM/PM\n- You can change the code with Claude to english and that is it.\n\nThis format must match exactly with the \"Fecha.Hora\" column in Google Sheets.",
        "height": 672,
        "width": 236
      },
      "id": "0ccc13be-c88d-4f29-9f28-0d83cfdf9107",
      "name": "Sticky Note 3",
