      ],
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 📝 Data Preparation\n\n**Extracts and organizes** post data:\n\n- Title (post title)\n- Copy (caption/description)\n- Status (current status)\n- video_url (Google Drive link)\n- is_drive_file (set to true)\n- row_number (for tracking)\n\nCleans and formats data for upload API.",
