        "content": "## 📊 Update Sheet Status\n\n**Marks post as published** in Google Sheets.\n\n**Changes:**\n- Status: \"Listo para postear\" → \"Posteado\"\n\n**Prevents:**\n- Duplicate posts\n- Re-processing same content\n\n**Matches by:** row_number column to ensure accurate update.",
